description	"General Maximilian Veers

Class Summary: 
A medic (Heals Armor) and commander class with a cloaking device, flamethrower, and rapid fire burst rifle.

Weaponry:
- EE-4 Carbine Rifle*
- Sonic Detonator (2)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
---EE-4 Carbine Rifle
- Based on DLT-20a level (3)
- Has reduced clipsize (5 burst fire shots before reloading)
- Deals damage similar to E-11 secodnary fire on full-auto and burst fire

Inventory:
- Cloaking Device
- Portable Bacta (25+ HP)
- Portable Large Bacta (50+ HP)

Attributes:
- Rally
- Blast Armor
- Fuel (2)
- Can view ally stats

Abilities:
- Can recover allies' armor (Press the 'Use' key while adjacent and facing teammate with depleted armor)
- Flamethrower
- Bounty Hunter style kicks and get-up rolls

General Veers is a stern and polished military man completely loyal to the New Order. Veers commanded the ground forces attached to Lord Vader's elite Imperial Death Squadron."